OL,3,C'A part of me is empty': Parents'
OL,4,Ctribute to young biker killed in crash
OL,6,FThe parents of a 24-year-old biker who
OL,7,Fdied after a crash in Torquay have
OL,8,Fpaid tribute to son with an
OL,9,F"infectious smile and laugh".
OL,11,FPolice officers were called to Torwood
OL,12,FStreet, Torquay, at around 5.05pm on
OL,13,FSunday 31 August to reports of the
OL,14,Fcollision involving a black Audi, a
OL,15,Fblue Suzuki motorcycle and a grey Ford
OL,16,FRanger.
OL,18,FThe motorcycle rider, Ben Rafton, died
OL,19,Fat the scene of the crash.
