OL,6,FBen was living in Southampton but was
OL,7,Foriginally from Plymouth.
OL,9,FIn a statement paying tribute to his
OL,10,Fson, Ben's father Barrie, said: "Ben,
OL,11,Ffrom the happy baby you were to the
OL,12,Ffine young man you grew into.
OL,14,F"The short time you were given in life
OL,15,Fhas been an extraordinary journey
OL,16,Ffilled with a number of adventures.
OL,18,F"Your magnetic personality, your
OL,19,Finfectious smile and laughter will be
OL,20,Fmissed by many.
OL,26,@rD@aOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
