OL,3,C'A part of me is empty': Parents'
OL,4,Ctribute to young biker killed in crash
OL,6,F"As your dad my heart has been broken
OL,7,Fand my battle will be difficult beyond
OL,8,Fwords.
OL,10,F"Sleep peacefully my precious youngest
OL,11,Fson, watch over us and keep us safe.
OL,12,FAlways in our hearts."
OL,14,FBen's mum Somaya, added: "I can't
OL,15,Fdescribe how much I miss my boy Ben.
OL,16,FWe spoke every day and FaceTimed
OL,17,Fpretty much 10 times within that day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@VO]vD@ZOU
