OL,3,C'A part of me is empty': Parents'
OL,4,Ctribute to young biker killed in crash
OL,6,F"Even though he didn't live near me it
OL,7,Fwas like he was down the road. He used
OL,8,Fto visit me all the time, it was never
OL,9,Fa chore for him to drive three hours
OL,10,Fdown and up in the same day.
OL,12,F"Where do I start to tell you how
OL,13,Famazing he was, not just to me but to
OL,14,Feverybody he met. He loved his
OL,15,Fbrothers and his dad, he loved his
OL,16,Fnieces and nephews - he just loved
OL,17,Fchildren even though he didn't have
OL,18,Fhis own.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
