OL,3,C'A part of me is empty': Parents'
OL,4,Ctribute to young biker killed in crash
OL,6,F"I knew if he ever had children he
OL,7,Fwould be the best daddy and would
OL,8,Falways be there for them through
OL,9,Feverything.
OL,11,F"Ben loved life, made me and everyone
OL,12,Faround him laugh, that was him, he
OL,13,Fjust wanted to make people happy.
OL,15,F"The last messages I had from him was
OL,16,F'I love you mum' which was him more
OL,17,Fthan once a day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
