OL,3,C'A part of me is empty': Parents'
OL,4,Ctribute to young biker killed in crash
OL,6,F"He was very generous and he would
OL,7,Falways buy his nieces and nephews
OL,8,Fridiculously expensive presents - but
OL,9,FBen loved to do that.
OL,11,F"Ben was a mummy's boy who just wanted
OL,12,Fme to be happy. He will be missed and
OL,13,Fa massive part of me is empty at this
OL,14,Fmoment.
OL,16,F"I hope in time I will be able to make
OL,17,Fsome sense of this tragedy but at the
OL,18,Fmoment, I can't even imagine how I
OL,19,Fwill get through today or tomorrow or
OL,20,Fever without him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
